<H2>Expressions rationnelles</H2>
<P class=3DexplicationExemple><SPAN class=3Dcode>grep</SPAN>, =
<SPAN>sed</SPAN>,=20
<SPAN class=3Dcode>find -regex</SPAN> utilisent des expressions =
rationnelles=20
<I>simples</I>.</P>
<P class=3DexplicationExemple><SPAN class=3Dcode>grep -e</SPAN>, <SPAN=20
class=3Dcode>awk</SPAN>, <SPAN class=3Dcode>perl</SPAN> utilisent des =
expressions=20
rationnelles <I>=E9tendues</I>.</P>
<H3>=C9l=E9ments communs </H3>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>\</SPAN> supprime la =
signification des=20
caract=E8res sp=E9ciaux,</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>prix=3D25\$</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>.</SPAN> remplace =
n'importe quel=20
caract=E8re,</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>g.n.rique</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>^</SPAN> repr=E9sente le =
d=E9but de=20
cha=EEne,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>$</SPAN> repr=E9sente la =
fin de=20
cha=EEne,</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>^$</P>
<P class=3DexplicationExemple>ligne vide</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>*</SPAN> indique z=E9ro, =
une ou=20
plusieurs occurrences,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>[ ]</SPAN> repr=E9sente =
une liste, un=20
intervalle ou une classe,</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>[e=E9=EA=E8=EB]</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>[0-9]</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>[[:upper:]]</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>\<I>i</I></SPAN> contenu =
du=20
<I>i</I><SUP>=E8me</SUP> regroupement entre parenth=E8ses.</P>
<H3>Classes de caract=E8res</H3>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>alpha</SPAN> caract=E8res=20
alphab=E9tiques,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>digit</SPAN> chiffres =
d=E9cimaux,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>xdigit</SPAN> chiffres=20
hexad=E9cimaux,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>alnum</SPAN> caract=E8res=20
alphanum=E9riques,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>lower</SPAN> =
minuscules,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>upper</SPAN> =
majuscules,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>blank</SPAN> caract=E8res =
blancs,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>space</SPAN> caract=E8res=20
s=E9parateurs,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>punct</SPAN> signes de=20
ponctuation,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>graph</SPAN> symboles =
visibles,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>print</SPAN> symboles =
visibles ou=20
blancs,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>cntrl</SPAN> caract=E8res =
de contr=F4le=20
d'impression.</P>
<H3>=C9l=E9ments des expressions rationnelles =E9tendues</H3>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>|</SPAN> repr=E9sente une=20
alternative,</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>Y|y</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>+</SPAN> r=E9clame une ou =
plusieurs=20
occurrences,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>?</SPAN> r=E9clame z=E9ro =
ou une=20
occurrence,</P>
<P class=3Dexemple>[+-]?[[:digit:]]+</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>{ }</SPAN> r=E9clament un =
certain nombre=20
de r=E9p=E9titions,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>( )</SPAN> regroupent des=20
=E9l=E9ments.</P>
<H3>=C9quivalences pour les expressions rationnelles simples</H3>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>\|</SPAN> correspond au =
<SPAN=20
class=3DlettreOption>|</SPAN> des expressions =E9tendues,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>\+</SPAN> correspond au =
<SPAN=20
class=3DlettreOption>+</SPAN> des expressions =E9tendues,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>\?</SPAN> correspond au =
<SPAN=20
class=3DlettreOption>?</SPAN> des expressions =E9tendues,</P>
<P class=3Doptions><SPAN class=3DlettreOption>\{ \}</SPAN> correspondent =
aux <SPAN=20
class=3DlettreOption>{}</SPAN> des expressions =E9tendues,</P>
